### ============================================================================
### PROFILE — /api/v1/profile
### ============================================================================

### Get my companies
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/profile/companies
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Get my profile
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Update my profile
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "first_name": "Dike",
  "last_name": "Thomas",
  "username": "dikethomas",
  "phone": "+2348012345678",
  "avatar_url": null,
  "profile_picture_option": "initials",
  "billing_currency": "NGN"
}

### Upload avatar (multipart)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/profile/avatar
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=avatar-boundary

--avatar-boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="avatar"; filename="avatar.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./test-avatar.jpg
--avatar-boundary--

### Change password
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/profile/password
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "current_password": "Str0ng!Pass123",
  "new_password": "NewStr0ng!Pass456"
}

### Upgrade plan
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/profile/upgrade-plan
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "plan_code": "PREMIUM"
}
